      public byte[] getContentLocation()
      Get Content-Location value.
      Returns:
      the value return PduPart.disposition[0] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 128> (Form-data). return PduPart.disposition[1] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 129> (Attachment). return PduPart.disposition[2] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 130> (Inline).

    • setContentDisposition

      public void setContentDisposition(byte[] contentDisposition)
      Set Content-Disposition value. Use PduPart.disposition[0] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 128> (Form-data). Use PduPart.disposition[1] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 129> (Attachment). Use PduPart.disposition[2] instead of invalid input: '<'Octet 130> (Inline).
      Parameters:
      contentDisposition - the value
